author: Erin Glover
title: Disney Parks After Dark: Main Street Electrical Parade Returns Home to Disneyland Park
text: It’s here! Tonight is the premiere of the return of the Main Street Electrical Parade to the place it began – Disneyland park. We captured this colorful photo during a recent rehearsal. The iconic parade officially begins its limited-time run tomorrow night, and will light up Main Street, U.S.A, through June 18. Don’t miss your chance to relive fond memories and make all-new ones during this special appearance.
